            "title": "Shipping Information",
            "content": "<p><strong>Just placed your order? 🎉 Great choice!</strong></p><p>Our team gets to work immediately to prepare your package with care.</p><p><strong>⏱️ Processing time:</strong> Within 24-48 hours</p><p>Once your order ships, you'll receive <strong>a confirmation email with your tracking number</strong>. With one click, you can follow your package all the way to your doorstep.</p><p>Questions? Our customer support team is available 7 days a week.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
